                <h2>БАЗОВІ КЛАСИ</h2>
                <ol>
                  <li><code><a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/android/view/View.html">View</a></code></li>
                  <li><code><a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/android/view/ViewGroup.html">ViewGroup</a></code></li>
                  <li><code><a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/android/view/ViewGroup.LayoutParams.html">ViewGroup.LayoutParams</a></code></li>
